column5: How can this......    Be turning into this... http://www.theweathernetwork.com/weather/CAON0663 ARRRGGG!!!!
when I first saw the Winter Warning I thought it was a website error! I have choice words for that little comedian called mother nature.
I was hoping for a nice weekend. I am going to North bay to visit my daughter for easter weekend and wanted to get some work done around her house.  Hey. are there smelts running there yet?
Im just not sure I want to drive to Barrie in that tomorrow...
Not yet ... but soon... one thing though.. ya can't fish for 'em legally in Nipissing or the tribs south of Hwy 17..  Randy

Everyone always acts so surprised when this happens.  We live in Northern Ontario, get used to it When I was in highschool/college we would go camping up near Rabbit Lake every May long weekend and it would snow every time without fail, it was just part of the experience.  With that said, the snow can go do dirty things to itself at this point!!  I'm done with winter...
Yes they are starting to run here...just not from Nip yet.
